languages.text: {n}Вистенца кривится от собственных воспоминаний.{/n} "Иные движения. Иные взгляды. Огромные глаза на неестественно искаженном лице, заостренные уши..."
{n}Vistenza cringes from the memories.{/n} "The strange movements. The strange looks. The abnormally large eyes on an unnaturally distorted face. The pointed ears..."

languages.text: {n}ヴィステンツァは何かを思い出し、身震いをした。{/n}「その奇妙な動き。奇妙な視線。不自然に歪んだ顔に以上に大きな目。尖った耳…」

languages.text: {n}Vistenza grimace en cherchant dans ses souvenirs.{/n} « Elle bouge de manière étrange. Elle a un regard déstabilisant, et ses yeux sont étonnamment grands. Son visage est déformé et ses oreilles sont pointues... »
languages.original_text: {n}Vistenza cringes from the memories.{/n} "The strange movements. The strange looks. The abnormally large eyes on an unnaturally distorted face. The pointed ears..."

languages.text: {n}维丝坦萨一边回忆着，一边皱起了眉头。{/n}“她的动作很古怪，样子也很古怪。她长着一张扭曲的怪脸，眼睛大得不正常，耳朵也是尖尖的……”
languages.original_text: {n}Vistenza cringes from the memories.{/n} "The strange movements. The strange looks. The abnormally large eyes on an unnaturally distorted face. The pointed ears..."

languages.text: {n}Vistenza se estremece de pensar en el tema.{/n} «Que se mueva tan raro. Que mire tan raro. Tiene los ojos enormes y la cara desproporcionada. Que sus orejas sean tan pronunciadas...».

languages.text: {n}Vistenza verzieht ob der Erinnerungen das Gesicht.{/n} "Die merkwürdigen Bewegungen. Das merkwürdige Aussehen. Die abnorm großen Augen auf einem unnatürlich verzerrten Gesicht. Die spitzen Ohren ..."

languages.text: {n}Vistenza hatırlayarak ürperiyor.{/n} "Garip hareketleri, tuhaf bakışları, gayritabii çarpık yüzündeki olağanüstü büyüklükteki gözleri, sivri kulakları..."
